\v 39 Lekhulusini lesango kwakukhona amatafula amabili ngapha, lamatafula amabili ngapha, ukuhlabela phezu kwawo umnikelo wokutshiswa\x + 46.2.\x*\x + Levi 1.3,9,13,14,17; Hez.40.42.\x* lomnikelo wesono\x + Levi 4.2,3; 42.13; 44.27; 46.20.\x* lomnikelo wecala\x + Levi 5.6; 6.6; 7.1; 42.13; 46.20.\x*.
\v 40 Laseceleni ngaphandle ekwenyukeleni kuso isivalo sesango lenyakatho kwakulamatafula amabili, laseceleni elinye elingasekhulusini lesango kwakulamatafula amabili.
\v 41 Amatafula amane ngapha, lamatafula amane ngapha, ngaseceleni kwesango; amatafula ayisificaminwembili, ababehlabela phezu kwawo\x + 40.39.\x*.
\v 42 Lamatafula amane omnikelo wokutshiswa\x + Levi 1.3,9,13,14,17; 40.42.\x* awamatshe abaziweyo\x + Eks. 20.25.\x*; ubude babuyingalo eyodwa lengxenye, lobubanzi babuyingalo eyodwa lengxenye, lokuphakama kwakuyingalo eyodwa. Phezu kwawo babeka izikhali abahlaba ngazo umnikelo wokutshiswa\x + Levi 1.3,9,13,14,17; 40.42.\x* lomhlatshelo.
\v 43 Kwakulezingwegwe\x + Hlab. 68.13; Gen. 49.14; Hlu. 5.16.\x*, eziyibubanzi besandla\x + 40.5.\x* sinye, zimisiwe ngaphakathi inhlangothi zonke ezizingelezeleyo; laphezu kwamatafula kwakulenyama yomnikelo.
