\v 44 Langaphandle kwesango elingaphakathi kwakulamakamelo\x + 40.17.\x* abahlabeleli egumeni elingaphakathi\x + 1 Lan. 6.31-33.\x*, elaliseceleni kwesango elisenyakatho, lokukhangela kwalo kusendleleni yeningizimu; elilodwa liseceleni kwesango eliseningizimu, likhangele ngasendleleni yenyakatho.
\v 45 Wasesithi kimi: Lelikamelo\x + 40.17.\x* okukhangela kwalo kusendleleni yeningizimu, lingelabapristi, abagcina umlindo wendlu\x + 44.8,14,15,16; 48.11; Levi 8.35; Nani 1.53.\x*.
\v 46 Lekamelo okukhangela kwalo kusendleleni yenyakatho lingelabapristi\x + 40.17.\x*\x + 42.4,11; 46.19.\x*, abagcina umlindo welathi\x + Nani 18.5.\x*. La\x + 43.19; 44.15,16; 48.11.\x* ngamadodana kaZadoki\x + 1 Kho. 2.35; 1 Lan. 24.3,6.\x* phakathi kwamadodana kaLevi, asondela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni ukuyikhonza\x + 43.19; 44.15,16; 48.11.\x*\x + 42.13; 45.4.\x*.
\v 47 Waselinganisa iguma; ubude baba zingalo ezilikhulu\x + 41.13-15.\x*, lobubanzi baba zingalo ezilikhulu\x + 41.13-15.\x*, lilingene inhlangothi zozine\x + 45.2; Isam. 21.16; 41.21; 43.16; 48.20.\x*; lelathi laliphambi kwendlu\x + 43.13.\x*.
